    <title>如何优雅的使用OneManager</title>
    <link href="https://blog.mcseekeri.top/archives/Guide-of-OneManager/"/>
    <id>https://blog.mcseekeri.top/archives/Guide-of-OneManager/</id>
    <published>2020-08-19T12:48:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-05-02T09:21:00.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" type="text&#x2F;css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/hexo-tag-hint@0.3.1/dist/hexo-tag-hint.min.css"><link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>鉴于我在OneManager群里当客服当的快吐了,而且逸笙前辈又死活不更新README,所以我专门抽出时间来写一个完全版本的OneManager教程。</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="原材料准备"><a href="#原材料准备" class="headerlink" title="原材料准备"></a>原材料准备</h2><ul><li>稳定的互联网接入</li><li>一台智能设备(电脑手机均可)</li><li>有科学上网的工具</li><li>好使的脑子</li></ul><h2 id="找到官方Repo"><a href="#找到官方Repo" class="headerlink" title="找到官方Repo"></a>找到官方Repo</h2><p>就目前来讲,OneManager在传播的过程中各大博客二次打包/Fork的简直不成样子了,所以经常有人用着旧版软件来咨询我们问题,殊不知这个Bug已经修复了大约114514年了（大嘘<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.3/ysun/7.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.3/ysun/7.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="暴躁内谁"></p><div class="note warning"><p>切记！OneManager只在Github上更新，除此之外任何地方的代码可用性都不做保证！</p></div><p>唯一官方指定Repo<a href="https://github.com/qkqpttgf/OneManager-php">在此</a>,别走丢了。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Github.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Github.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="Repo截图，存档于2020.8.19"><br>下文我就把OneManager简称OM了啊。</p><h2 id="选择你的平台"><a href="#选择你的平台" class="headerlink" title="选择你的平台"></a>选择你的平台</h2><p>因为逸笙前辈<del>不想被我们骂万年不更新</del>为了增加OM的平台兼容性,所以兼容了一大波网络服务,算是各有优缺点罢,下面我整理了一下,你自己看着选。</p><h3 id="Heroku"><a href="#Heroku" class="headerlink" title="Heroku"></a><a href="https://heroku.com/">Heroku</a></h3><div class='checkbox plus green checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>部署最简单 真正一键式</p>            </div><div class='checkbox plus green checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>使用无需付费</p>            </div><div class='checkbox minus red checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>配置过程需要科学上网</p>            </div><div class='checkbox minus red checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>绑定域名需要信用卡(可通过反向代理绕过)</p>            </div><h3 id="腾讯云函数"><a href="#腾讯云函数" class="headerlink" title="腾讯云函数"></a><a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/product/scf">腾讯云函数</a></h3><div class='checkbox plus green checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>访问速度快</p>            </div><div class='checkbox plus green checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>自选地点丰富</p>            </div><div class='checkbox minus red checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>按量付费，如果没做好反DDCC很容易倾家荡产</p>            </div><div class='checkbox minus red checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>绑定域名需要经过备案</p>            </div><div class='checkbox minus red checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>环境变量大小有限，理论上最多只能添加四个盘</p>            </div><h3 id="华为函数工作流"><a href="#华为函数工作流" class="headerlink" title="华为函数工作流"></a><a href="https://console.huaweicloud.com/functiongraph">华为函数工作流</a></h3><div class='checkbox plus green checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>程序不部署在中国大陆时绑定域名无需备案</p>            </div><div class='checkbox minus red checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>环境变量大小有限，理论上最多只能添加两个盘</p>            </div><p>其余同腾讯云函数</p><h3 id="阿里函数计算"><a href="#阿里函数计算" class="headerlink" title="阿里函数计算"></a><a href="https://fc.console.aliyun.com/">阿里函数计算</a></h3><div class='checkbox plus green checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>环境变量大小无限制</p>            </div><p>其余同华为函数工作流</p><h3 id="百度云函数计算"><a href="#百度云函数计算" class="headerlink" title="百度云函数计算"></a><a href="https://console.bce.baidu.com/cfc/#/cfc/functions">百度云函数计算</a></h3><div class='checkbox plus green checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>有免费额度，完全足够使用</p>            </div><p>其余同腾讯云函数</p><h3 id="自家VPS或虚拟空间"><a href="#自家VPS或虚拟空间" class="headerlink" title="自家VPS或虚拟空间"></a>自家VPS或虚拟空间</h3><div class='checkbox plus green checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>你说呢</p>            </div><div class='checkbox minus red checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>你说呢</p>            </div><h2 id="开始部署"><a href="#开始部署" class="headerlink" title="开始部署"></a>开始部署</h2><p>总之,在选好平台之后就该开始安装程序力！<br>因为OM不管部署在哪里,安装过程都差不多,所以这里先分开讲不同平台怎么部署<del>，之后糊弄一下安装过程就可以啦</del><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.3/ysun/2.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.3/ysun/2.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="名   言   警   句"></p><del>点点点就完了有啥难度</del><h3 id="Heroku部署"><a href="#Heroku部署" class="headerlink" title="Heroku部署"></a>Heroku部署</h3><p>打开Repo你应该能看到那个裂了的图,点那个Deploy就成了。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Heroku.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Heroku.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="没梯子就是这么可怜"><br>然后会跳转到Heroku,记得带上梯子和脑子,安装之前需要注册账号,这里我略过不讲。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.3/ysun/34.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.3/ysun/34.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>然后你就会看到配置页面,起名,选地点,点Deploy app,搞定!<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Heroku-Deploy.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Heroku-Deploy.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="我们是OM,不是隔壁OneIndex"><br>然后就是点点点。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Install.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Install.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Heroku-APIKey.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Heroku-APIKey.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="申请了填进去就好"></p><h3 id="腾讯云函数部署"><a href="#腾讯云函数部署" class="headerlink" title="腾讯云函数部署"></a>腾讯云函数部署</h3><p>点击Repo里那个又大又绿的下载按钮。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Download.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Download.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="点就完了"><br>然后选择”Download ZIP”,当然你能Clone也行。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Download-ZIP.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Download-ZIP.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>下载下来之后解压,然后点开目录,Ctrl+A选择所有文件,打包。</p><span class='p red'>没这个过程你程序大概率部署失败，别来找我售后</span><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.3/ysun/44.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.3/ysun/44.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>然后奔向<a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/product/scf">腾讯云函数官网</a><br>注册账号不解释。<br>左上角选好地点,然后点击新建函数。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>推荐空白模板,但偏要选另外一个我也没办法,反正不管是啥都要被干掉换成OM的代码。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.3/ysun/16.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.3/ysun/16.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>上传你二次打包的压缩包,不解释。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF2.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF2.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>左边点触发管理,新建触发,按照图片设置。</p><div class="note warning"><p>务必勾选”启用集成响应”</p></div><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF-API.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF-API.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>然后去安装程序。记得新建SecretId和SecretKey。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF-Install.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF-Install.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="反正不管选哪个都是要花点钱的"><br>我建议你新建个只能访问SCF和API的账户,安全第一。<br>新建访问密钥的那个页面侧边栏,点用户,新建用户<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF-NewUser.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF-NewUser.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="务必记得开编程访问"><br>然后把SecretId和SecretKey填回去,搞定。</p><p>如果你需要自定义域名,那就要回到API设置那个地方,点开”管理API”,点编辑,然后把路径删到只剩下个斜杠。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF-API-Config.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF-API-Config.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>一路下一步,之后回到”服务信息”那里,把API发布一下。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF-API2.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF-API2.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="光看气势你们已经输了"><br>“自定义域名”那里新建域名。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF-Domain.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/SCF-Domain.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>如果需要SSL,可以用Cloudflare的源服务器证书,也可以去腾讯申请个TrustAsia证书。</p><h2 id="程序安装"><a href="#程序安装" class="headerlink" title="程序安装"></a>程序安装</h2><p>之后就是枯燥无味的安装了,因为在几乎所有平台上OM表现都几乎一致<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Install.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Install.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>总之跟着步骤来,该添加API的添加API,该复制的复制。</p><h2 id="配置详解"><a href="#配置详解" class="headerlink" title="配置详解"></a>配置详解</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Full-Setting.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.4/post/Guide-of-OneManager/Full-Setting.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>嗯……因为这里很多的说明都是祖传代码了,可能不易理解,所以我简单翻译下。</p><h3 id="平台变量"><a href="#平台变量" class="headerlink" title="平台变量"></a>平台变量</h3><ul><li>adminloginpage</li></ul><p>隐藏登录按钮,只能通过访问[你的域名]/?[设置的内容]来打开管理界面</p><blockquote><p>示例: login<br>访问:<a href="https://example.com/?login">https://example.com/?login</a></p></blockquote><ul><li>autoJumpFirstDisk</li></ul><p>添加多盘时加一个跳转,不设置的话访问根目录时会让你选择哪个盘,设为1会自动打开第一个盘。</p><ul><li>background</li></ul><p>背景图片,建议使用<a href="https://7bu.top/">去不图床</a>,速度和稳定性都有保证,上传完把链接丢过来</p><blockquote><p>示例: <a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.3/img/FutureGadgetLab.webp">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mcseekeri@1.2.3/img/FutureGadgetLab.webp</a></p></blockquote><ul><li>backgroundm</li></ul><p>同上,只不过是给手机准备的。</p><ul><li>customCss</li></ul><p>自定义CSS格式,一般用户直接无视就好</p><ul><li>customScript</li></ul><p>在每个页面里插入JS脚本,可以放统计代码啥的。<br>因为屑逸笙没写多行处理,所以你直接在别的地方写完复制到这就行</p><blockquote><p>示例: <code>&lt;script&gt;   window.ga_tid = &#39;UA-104605102-3&#39;;   (function() &#123;     var dga = document.createElement(&quot;script&quot;);     dga.src = &quot;https://rmt.dogedoge.com/fetch/public/ga.js&quot;;     var s = document.getElementsByTagName(&quot;script&quot;)[0];     s.parentNode.insertBefore(dga, s);   &#125;)(); &lt;/script&gt;</code></p></blockquote><div class="note warning"><p>部分主题并没有对这个选项做兼容,所以我个人推荐使用renexmoe主题</p></div><ul><li>passfile</li></ul><p>保存密码的文件名…不是密码！<br>更不是全站加密！<br>譬如罢,你把这个设置成<code>.password</code>,然后去加密某个目录,OM就会在你的OneDrive里创建一个叫<code>.password</code>的文件,里面是这个文件夹的密码。<br>所以设置好了不要轻易改,一改你原本的密码文件就可以看作失效了（<br>而且为了兼容性,我个人建议设置为<code>.password</code>就好,因为诸如GDIndex,GoIndex之类的目录程序都把这个作为密码文件名。</p><ul><li>theme</li></ul><p>选renexmoe.html！</p><p>186记得给我广告费。</p><h3 id="盘内变量"><a href="#盘内变量" class="headerlink" title="盘内变量"></a>盘内变量</h3><ul><li>domain_path</li></ul><p>不同的域名将不同的目录作为根目录…概念有点绕…<br>如果是Heroku部署且没绑卡,这个变量毫无作用…其他云函数平台可以</p><blockquote><p>示例: example.com:/默认/|bangumi.example.com:/番剧/|movie.example.com:/电影/|nsfw.example.com:/小姐姐/</p></blockquote><ul><li>downloadencrypt</li></ul><p>简单说,就是是否可以无需密码下载加密目录里的文件。</p><p>比如你有个加密文件夹”NSFW”,里面有个文件叫186526.mkv。<br>别人打开目录是啥也看不见的,毕竟他们没密码,但是你可以给他们<code>https://example.com/NSFW/186526.mkv</code>这个链接让他们下载目录里的文件。<br>近似于*nix系统中对目录rwx与-wx的区别</p><ul><li>guestup_path</li></ul><p>把某个文件夹设置成游客上传,文件夹内容不会展示,游客上传文件后可以拿到链接。<br>顺带一提文件会被强制重命名为文件的md5</p><div class="note warning"><p>不要想着提建议说删掉自动重命名,我2年前就提过多次,屑逸笙就是不改（叹气</p></div><blockquote><p>示例: /NSFW/186526/</p></blockquote><ul><li>public_path</li></ul><p>设置某个目录为全站根目录。</p><blockquote><p>示例:/NSFW</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>没有提到的配置项大多数不需要说明,或者一般用户用不着（</p></blockquote><h2 id="特殊玩法"><a href="#特殊玩法" class="headerlink" title="特殊玩法"></a>特殊玩法</h2>]]></content>
    
    
